4fd220ccf51b3e2876f6341def5030","tid":17680,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"夠撚膽就買返Jolla出返Meego"},{"pid":"3ea4f52685b7524b1cdbc8058410016613b14f1f","tid":17680,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果Nokia 知d客要乜<br />\n就唔會搵到今日咁<br />\n完全唔會有期望</blockquote><br />\n東山再起既例子唔係無既，不過真係要搵個好既ceo</blockquote><br />\nMotorola當年部Milestone<br />\n出左之後起死回生<br />\n不過之後又極速沒落<br />\n呢個就係android市場特點<br />\n用家品牌忠誠度唔高<br />\n以前未係智能手機年代<br />\n用開一個品牌就唔會成日轉<br />\n而家得android/iOS<br />\n既然大家都係用android<br />\n我唔一定要用死呢個牌子"},{"pid":"7187ad94ccddcfb4b3f76097a091dc991d24e16a","tid":17680,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後會唔會比黑警列作危險武器"},{"pid":"233b914cb5ab666bad793c4822071a3fd14a1626","tid":17680,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:19:13.000Z","msg":"唔係無得諗  <br />\n反正廚師添已經了無新意<br />\n向磚頭廠雄心萬丈既情況下話唔定可以激起千重浪<br />\n為智能電話市場帶黎一番新景象"},{"pid":"c2bd19a98028229b91750f8cd325049e47b7ac1c","tid":17680,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"nokia 用android 的話唔係無可能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573d045fe23da8cc6a4c80fa4bd4cd8f5035188a","tid":17680,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係無得諗  <br />\n反正廚師添已經了無新意<br />\n向磚頭廠雄心萬丈既情況下話唔定可以激起千重浪<br />\n為智能電話市場帶黎一番新景象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充<br />\n<br />\n廚師已經無晒新意<br />\n三叔又內哄緊<br />\n<br />\n如果真係比磚頭打返入黎依個市場話唔定真係一件好事"}]}